t another new\nformulae for Mathieu's eigenvalue relating the latter to a solution of certain\nBethe-like equation are found.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Jul 2014 16:21:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
