, for things that both technologies can do. Also included is\na brief description of some initial trials that the system has undergone and\nthe lessons learned (and plans laid) based on those early \"customer\"\nengagements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jul 2014 04:29:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-03"}
