ate the approach on\ntag refinement and localization on DUT-WEBV, a large dataset of web videos, and\nshow state-of-the-art results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jul 2014 15:48:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Apr 2015 18:12:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 May 2015 17:12:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-09"}
